Dialogue: 0,00:21:27.46,00:21:29.75,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凌晨四点
Dialogue: 0,00:21:30.50,00:21:32.75,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为何还没入睡
Dialogue: 0,00:21:32.75,00:21:35.38,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这糟糕的日子 听着"Bye Bye Black Birds"
Dialogue: 0,00:21:35.46,00:21:39.18,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自言自语也无法消除不安
Dialogue: 0,00:21:40.01,00:21:41.80,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}最近几个小时
Dialogue: 0,00:21:41.97,00:21:45.14,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我总是不断哭泣  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,00:21:46.60,00:21:49.81,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你在这里
Dialogue: 0,00:21:51.98,00:21:56.49,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看你给我的那些信
Dialogue: 0,00:21:56.61,00:22:02.41,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每读一遍  痛苦都会消失
Dialogue: 0,00:22:02.74,00:22:05.66,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:22:05.87,00:22:08.41,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:22:08.62,00:22:14.67,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  相信着你
Dialogue: 0,00:22:14.92,00:22:20.80,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,00:22:21.01,00:22:25.60,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:22:25.85,00:22:27.43,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:22:27.43,00:22:30.19,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:22:30.44,00:22:33.19,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:22:33.31,00:22:39.32,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  你就在我心中
Dialogue: 0,00:22:39.57,00:22:45.37,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,00:22:45.58,00:22:50.25,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:22:50.46,00:22:52.54,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:02:23.40,00:02:28.74,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}指引着我  前往远方
Dialogue: 0,00:02:28.94,00:02:37.13,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一路披荆斩棘  杀出血路
Dialogue: 0,00:02:39.37,00:02:42.31,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yo guess who’s back Everybody get down
Dialogue: 0,00:02:42.38,00:02:45.11,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}guess who’s back hey step up step up!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.86,00:03:00.20,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被命运捉弄  I’m falling down
Dialogue: 0,00:03:00.47,00:03:05.60,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你同奏的和声  再也不会响起
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.67,00:03:10.80,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你强烈的香气还在心头萦绕
Dialogue: 0,00:03:11.58,00:03:13.93,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不愿再继续等待
Dialogue: 0,00:03:15.40,00:03:17.15,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hey guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:03:17.48,00:03:20.77,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}带着愿望
Dialogue: 0,00:03:20.77,00:03:22.52,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)} guess who’s back
